<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Content Balance Analyzer</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- UMD builds guaranteed to work globally on Squarespace -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/compromise@14.14.3/builds/compromise.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.1/dist/chart.umd.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        
        #cba-wrapper { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: transparent; }
        #cba-wrapper .glass-panel { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8); }
        #cba-wrapper .score-card { transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease; }
        @media (min-width: 1024px) { #cba-wrapper .score-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } }

        /* Highlight Colors */
        #cba-wrapper .personal-word { color: #00B700; font-weight: 600; background-color: rgba(0, 183, 0, 0.1); padding: 0 2px; border-radius: 3px; }
        #cba-wrapper .visual-word { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: #ef4444; text-underline-offset: 2px; background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05); padding: 0 2px; border-radius: 3px; }
        #cba-wrapper .overlap-word { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgba(0, 183, 0, 0.15); border-bottom: 2px solid #ef4444; padding: 0 2px; border-radius: 3px; }
        
        /* Accordion Animations */
        .cba-accordion-content { transition: max-height 0.3s ease-in-out, opacity 0.3s ease-in-out; max-height: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; }
        .cba-accordion-open { max-height: 500px; opacity: 1; margin-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="cba-wrapper" class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:py-8 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
        <header class="mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Content Balance Analyzer</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm sm:text-base px-2">Analyze complexity, personal narrative, and visual imagery.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- SINGLE COLUMN FEED LAYOUT -->
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
            
            <!-- 1. Text Input Section -->
            <div class="glass-panel p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm transition-all duration-300">
                <label for="cba-inputText" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">Paste text or record live audio</label>
                <div id="cba-errorMsg" class="hidden mb-3 text-sm font-medium text-red-500 bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-red-200 shadow-sm"></div>

                <!-- Prominent Audio Buttons -->
                <div id="cba-audioControls" class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <button id="cba-recordBtn" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-rose-600 text-white hover:bg-rose-700 font-bold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md active:scale-95">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"></path></svg>
                        Record Audio
                    </button>
                    <button id="cba-transcribeBtn" class="hidden flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white hover:bg-indigo-700 font-bold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md active:scale-95">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path></svg>
                        Stop & Transcribe
                    </button>
                    <!-- Audio Timer -->
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm h-[44px]">
                        <div id="cba-recordingIndicator" class="hidden relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
                            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-rose-400 opacity-75"></span>
                            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-rose-600"></span>
                        </div>
                        <span id="cba-timerDisplay" class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 tracking-wider">00:00</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <textarea id="cba-inputText" class="w-full h-64 sm:h-80 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent outline-none resize-none transition-all text-slate-700 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base bg-white/50" placeholder="Start typing, paste text, or record your voice...&#10;&#10;Tip: if you finish recording while a pop up is active, it may not transcribe."></textarea>
                
                <!-- Redesigned Action Buttons -->
                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <button id="cba-analyzeBtn" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md active:scale-95 disabled:opacity-50">
                        Refresh Analysis
                    </button>
                    
                    <button id="cba-clearBtn" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 font-semibold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-sm active:scale-95">
                        Clear
                    </button>

                    <button id="cba-copyBtn" class="hidden w-full sm:w-auto bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50 font-semibold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-sm active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-1M8 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M8 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 0h2a2 2 0 012 2v3m2 4H10m0 0l3-3m-3 3l3 3"></path></svg>
                        <span id="cba-copyBtnText">Copy Report</span>
                    </button>

                    <!-- Subtle Dictionary Status Indicator -->
                    <div class="w-full sm:w-auto sm:ml-auto flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-end gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500">
                        <span id="cba-dictDot" class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                        <span id="cba-dictText">Loading Dictionaries...</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- ALL RESULTS CONTAINER -->
            <!-- The hidden class is removed so the dashboard is visible immediately -->
            <div id="cba-resultsContainer" class="flex flex-col space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
                
                <!-- 2. SCORE SUMMARY DASHBOARD -->
                <div id="cba-summaryCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-t-4 border-slate-800 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4 border-b pb-2 border-slate-100">Score Summary</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <!-- Content -->
                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-100 pb-1">Content</h3>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Personal:</span> <span id="sum-personal" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0%</span> <span id="sum-personal-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Visual:</span> <span id="sum-visual" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0%</span> <span id="sum-visual-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Intangible:</span> <span id="sum-intangible" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0%</span> <span id="sum-intangible-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Delivery -->
                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-100 pb-1">Delivery</h3>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Words/min:</span> <span id="sum-wpm" class="font-bold text-slate-800">-</span> <span id="sum-wpm-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Syllable/sec:</span> <span id="sum-sps" class="font-bold text-slate-800">-</span> <span id="sum-sps-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Pause %:</span> <span id="sum-pause" class="font-bold text-slate-800">-</span> <span id="sum-pause-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Simplicity -->
                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-slate-100 pb-1">Simplicity</h3>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Words/Sent:</span> <span id="sum-wps" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0</span> <span id="sum-wps-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Comp. Grade:</span> <span id="sum-grade" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0.0</span> <span id="sum-grade-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-sm"><span class="text-slate-600">Simple %:</span> <span id="sum-simple" class="font-bold text-slate-800">0%</span> <span id="sum-simple-eval" class="text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wide bg-slate-100 text-slate-500">Waiting</span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 3. Tangible Text Map -->
                <div id="cba-highlightContainer" class="glass-panel p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center mb-4 border-b pb-3 border-slate-100 gap-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">Tangible Text Map</h3>
                            <div class="group relative z-50">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                <div class="absolute left-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                    Green text represents Personal content (a specific person doing a specific thing). Red text represents Visual content (things people can see, like colours, sizes, groups, or common objects).
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-600 font-medium">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded bg-[#00B700]/10 border border-[#00B700]"></span> Personal</div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded bg-red-500/10 border-b border-red-500"></span> Visual (Underlined)</div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-3 h-3 rounded bg-[#00B700]/10 border-b-2 border-red-500"></span> Overlap</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="cba-highlightedText" class="w-full h-64 sm:h-80 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white overflow-y-auto text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base italic">Waiting for text...</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 4. Audio Metrics Grid (WPM Pace & Mumble Meter) -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
                    <!-- WPM Pace Card -->
                    <div id="cba-wpmCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-300 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-50">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start cursor-pointer" id="cba-wpmToggleBtn">
                            <div class="w-full">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Speaking Pace</h3>
                                    <div class="group relative z-50">
                                        <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                        <div class="absolute right-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                            Speaking more than 150wpm on average puts a strain on audience listening and comprehension. 120 plus or minus 20 is the gold standard.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                                    <div id="cba-wpmScore" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-400">0</div>
                                    <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">WPM Avg</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 text-slate-400 transition-transform duration-300 transform flex-shrink-0" id="cba-wpmArrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div id="cba-wpmAccordion" class="cba-accordion-content border-t border-slate-100 pt-2">
                            <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 mb-2 uppercase font-bold tracking-wide">Pace per 20-second interval</p>
                            <canvas id="cba-wpmChart" height="150"></canvas>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Mumble Meter Card -->
                    <div id="cba-mumbleCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-300 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-50">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Mumble Meter</h3>
                            <div class="group relative z-50">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                <div class="absolute right-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                    If you speak faster than 5 syllables per second, you're likely to make comprehension difficult for most people, particularly children, ESL, or audiences learning new concepts.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                            <div id="cba-mumbleScore" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-400">0.0</div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Syllables / Sec</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative w-full h-2.5 rounded-full mt-5" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #10b981, #f97316, #ef4444);">
                            <div id="cba-mumbleMarker" class="absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-3 h-5 bg-white border-2 border-slate-700 rounded-sm shadow-md transition-all duration-500" style="left: 0%; margin-left: -0.375rem;"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p id="cba-mumbleInterpret" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mt-3 text-slate-500">Waiting for Audio...</p>
                        <p id="cba-mumbleStats" class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">0.0s active / 0.0s pause / 0.0s total</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 5. SCORE CARDS GRID (Balances the remaining detailed cards) -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
                    
                    <!-- Personal Balance -->
                    <div id="cba-personalCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-300 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Personal Balance</h3>
                            <div class="group relative z-50">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                <div class="absolute right-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                    The best science communicators, podcasters, keynote speakers, etc, have extraordinarily high percentages (30% to 60%) of content about specific people doing specific things. This is the stuff of character driven story.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2"><div id="cba-personalScore" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-400">0%</div><span class="text-sm text-slate-500">of text</span></div>
                        <div class="relative w-full mt-4">
                            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -top-1.5 w-0.5 h-5 bg-slate-300 z-10 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-slate-100 h-2 rounded-full overflow-hidden"><div id="cba-personalProgress" class="h-full transition-all duration-500 bg-slate-300" style="width: 0%"></div></div>
                        </div>
                        <p id="cba-personalInterpret" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mt-3 text-slate-600">Waiting...</p>
                        <p id="cba-personalCount" class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">0 out of 0 words</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Visual Balance -->
                    <div id="cba-visualCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-300 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Visual Balance</h3>
                            <div class="group relative z-50">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                <div class="absolute right-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                    The best science communicators, podcasters, keynote speakers, etc, have moderate percentages (20% to 40%) of content about things people can see. This is the stuff of using concepts familiar to audiences to explain new ideas.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2"><div id="cba-visualScore" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-400">0%</div><span class="text-sm text-slate-500">of text</span></div>
                        <div class="relative w-full mt-4">
                            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -top-1.5 w-0.5 h-5 bg-slate-300 z-10 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-slate-100 h-2 rounded-full overflow-hidden"><div id="cba-visualProgress" class="h-full transition-all duration-500 bg-slate-300" style="width: 0%"></div></div>
                        </div>
                        <p id="cba-visualInterpret" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium mt-3 text-slate-600">Waiting...</p>
                        <p id="cba-visualCount" class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">0 out of 0 words</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Signal-Noise Ratio Card -->
                    <div id="cba-snCard" class="score-card glass-panel p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-slate-300 shadow-sm transition-colors duration-300">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-1">
                            <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Signal-Noise Ratio</h3>
                            <div class="group relative z-50">
                                <span class="flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded cursor-help">💡 Tip</span>
                                <div class="absolute right-0 w-56 sm:w-64 p-3 mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none font-normal normal-case tracking-normal z-50">
                                    If every sentence is trying to make one point, then the more words needed to make that point dilute and weaken the message. Sentences over 15 words on average have a message that is likely to require audiences to make their own interpretations; risking a lack of mutual understanding.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                            <div id="cba-snScore" class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-400">0.0</div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Avg words/sentence</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative w-full mt-4">
                            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -top-1.5 w-0.5 h-5 bg-slate-300 z-10 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
                            <div class="w-full bg-slate-100 h-2 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                                <div id="cba-snProgress" class="h-full transition-all duration-500 bg-slate-300" style="width: 0%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-3 cursor-pointer" id="cba-snToggleBtn">
                            <p id="cba-snInterpret" class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-slate-600">Waiting...</p>
                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 bg-slate-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors">More Metrics</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div id="cba-snAccordion" class="cba-accordion-content border-t border-slate-100 pt-3">
                            <div class="space-y-2 text-xs mb-5">
